member.example:
The following example illustrates the verifications of two strings being equal.  
If they are different, an exception is thrown.

Diagnostic.Diagnose(delegate(Diagnostic s)
{
    string tmp = "hello";
    if (tmp != "world")
        s.Error("The strings are not equal");
});

